    <h1 class="page-header-title">How Sigil works.</h1>
    <p class="hero-lede" style="margin-top:20px;max-width:760px">
      Sigil is a merge policy engine for agent-generated pull requests. It turns markdown specs into sealed CI evaluations and returns ALLOW, REVIEW, or BLOCK decisions your team can audit.
